{"tid":469792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"津巴布韋危機：總統穆加貝遭軟禁","createTime":"2017-11-15T16:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T16:11:01.000Z","uid":47265,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"507ccc9f6dddabada33bc41ca358a8a4daf14bfc","tid":469792,"uid":47265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"唔知駙馬爺有無好擔心呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n津巴布韋政治危機日益加深，總統穆加貝周三（11月15日）現時被軍隊軟禁。<br />\n<br />\n南非總統府發表聲明稱，總統祖馬與穆加貝通了話。祖馬將以「南部非洲發展共同體」（Southern African Development Community）主席的身份，派特使去津巴布韋斡旋。<br />\n<br />\n津巴布韋早前已接管首都哈拉雷的國家電視台（ZBC）總部。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中國外交部發言人耿爽在例行記者會上指，津巴布韋前副總統「沒有來中國」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-41992992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-41992992&d=wRYxnbutjtFT%2FkEIN6DJLNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a18ec4de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-41992992&h=1bce3814\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-41992992</a>"}]}